.SH "NAME"
sk_ns_capable \- General socket capability test
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'bool\ sk_ns_capable('u
.BI "bool sk_ns_capable(const\ struct\ sock\ *\ " "sk" ", struct\ user_namespace\ *\ " "user_ns" ", int\ " "cap" ");"
.SH "ARGUMENTS"
.PP
\fIsk\fR
.RS 4
Socket to use a capability on or through
.RE
.PP
\fIuser_ns\fR
.RS 4
The user namespace of the capability to use
.RE
.PP
\fIcap\fR
.RS 4
The capability to use
.RE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Test to see if the opener of the socket had when the socket was created and the current process has the capability
\fIcap\fR
in the user namespace
\fIuser_ns\fR\&.
